column5: DOMAIN IS IN THE PROCESS OF BEING ATTACHED!
If you have just attached the domain to the website, wait 15 minutes.
If you are the owner of the website and you can still see this error,
it means the domain attachment process hasn't been finished.
You need to finish it in the ""Domain Attachment"" section of Control Panel.
